volume.name: Pink Flamingos: Bring Down the Night

description:
Spider-Man battles alongside Captain America and the Avengers against the diabolical Serpent Society.

Plus, Spider-Man and the Human Torch are trapped on a space station full of Octo-Zombies plummeting toward the Earth. The best buds super team-up is running out of air and running out of time.

Also, classic adventure as Doctor Octopus reveals his diabolical plan to his NEW and DEADLY Sinister Six. Will Spidey be able to thwart Ock’s scheme in time?!

Includes material reprinted from Avenging Spider-Man #5, Amazing Spider-Man #680, Amazing Spider-Man #337!

Alfred would rather not get caught between a corrupt police force and a band of rebels, but a young Bruce Wayne is determined to save the young girl caught between that same rock and hard place. "I Hate It When He Does That" part 2.
name: I Hate it When He Does That
